    {
      "document_id": "doc-wt-001",
      "filename": "referral-optometry-2025-04-28.txt",
      "document_type": "referral_letter",
      "document_date": "2025-04-28",
      "received_date": "2025-04-28",
      "received_method": "fax",
      "content": {
        "format": "text",
        "text_content": "CENTRAL FLORIDA OPTOMETRY GROUP\n880 Lake Baldwin Lane, Orlando, FL 32814\nPhone: (407) 555-4410 | Fax: (407) 555-4411\n\nDate: April 28, 2025\n\nRE: URGENT RETINA REFERRAL\n\nPatient Name: William R. Thompson\nDate of Birth: 08/22/1946 (78 years old)\nPhone: (407) 555-2318\n\nDear Dr. Morrison,\n\nI am urgently referring Mr. William Thompson for retina evaluation of suspected exudative macular degeneration in the right eye.\n\nHISTORY:\nMr. Thompson reports that straight lines appear bent and there is a gray smudge near the center of his vision in the right eye, first noticed approximately two weeks ago. He denies pain, flashes, or floaters. He is anxious to protect his reading and driving vision.\n\nEXAMINATION TODAY:\nBest corrected visual acuity: OD 20/50 (previously 20/25 at his 2024 exam), OS 20/30.\nAmsler grid: central distortion OD; OS unremarkable.\nDilated exam: OD - numerous soft drusen with a grayish subfoveal elevation and trace subretinal fluid suspected at the macula. OS - numerous soft drusen, no hemorrhage, no elevation. The left eye shows numerous soft drusen consistent with intermediate dry AMD.\n\nIMPRESSION:\nFindings highly suspicious for neovascular (wet) age-related macular degeneration in the right eye. Intermediate dry AMD in the left eye.\n\nMEDICAL HISTORY (per patient):\n- Hyperlipidemia on atorvastatin\n- Former smoker, quit 1998\n- Taking AREDS2 vitamin supplement since 2024\n\nREQUEST:\nOCT and evaluation for anti-VEGF therapy at your earliest availability. Patient has been counseled on the urgency.\n\nThank you for seeing him promptly.\n\nSincerely,\nJames Liu, OD\nCentral Florida Optometry Group",
        "ocr_quality": 0.94
      },
      "extracted_data": {
        "referring_provider": {
          "name": "James Liu, OD",
